description:
Proper Japanese Title: 鉄漫 Tekken Comic

A humourous manga series based on Namco's popular fighting game franchise.

The comic follows vigilante schoolgirl Asuka Kazama as she attempts to rein in her megalomaniacal cousin Jin, and contend with threats at home. While the series is predominantly focused on Asuka and her rival Lili, subplots display Jin's activities, as well as those of other Tekken characters.

Authored by Takato Rui, and published by Ultra Jump, new chapters could originally be found free to read on the Ultra Jump Egg website(and in English), though these were later taken down when the chapters were collected together for printed editions.
name: Tetsuman - Tekken Comic

description:
30 year-old virgin, Sal Ghesboro, travels back in time to preemptively impregnate the mom of his worst childhood tormentor; TIME F*CKING him out of existence!

Time Fucker is a digital comic by Joe Infurnari that is published through a dedicated website and Trip City. This print version collects the first four chapters of Time Fucker and the storyline "I'm Taking this Laying Down!, Part 1-4" respectively. It was first published online in April 2012.

There are two different print versions, the standard edition and the deluxe "black sac" edition that was shipped in a black ziploc bag along with original ink sketches and a Time Fucker button. These print editions were limited to 200 and 100 copies respectively.
name: Time Fucker
